#: ../../modules/digital/digital_hardware.rst:18
msgid ""
"``grouped``: Applies all single-qubit gates first, followed by all two-"
"qubit gates."
msgstr ""
"``grouped``: Aplica primer totes les portes d'un sol qubit, seguides de "
"totes les portes de dos qubits."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_hardware.rst:19
msgid "``interposed``: Interleaves single and two-qubit gates."
msgstr "``interposed``: Intercala les portes d'un sol qubit i de dos qubits."

